    <item>
      <title>Dimensional Instability AA - please .. tweak</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Wizards&amp;message.id=3537#M3537</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;I thought this would be a really cool AA, I mean the idea was great...&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Implementation ...well , a tweak and it would be prefect.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;background:&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I bought this last night, not really sure how it would work..&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;so in Icefall, i clicked my freshly made hotkey, and poof I was gone .. I went from the Goblin camp near the spires, to the middle of the Mammoth field.. stood there for a tick , and poof gone again ..this time appearing in the Mammoth watering hole.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Conclusion. That is a&amp;nbsp;pretty FAR distance to warp to.. thank god nothing was KoS where I landed, as this aa&amp;nbsp;could be a death wish as it is currently implemented.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I'm not really sure&amp;nbsp;where I'd use this aa now...&amp;nbsp; I thought it would be more warping in very tight&amp;nbsp;pattern.. like with 10 feet of target or 5 feet of the initial point of origin.. I mean the only reason this so far lives up to the expectation of more melee mitigation, is because it follows the path of enlightenment that states " If you don't want to be hit, don't be there"&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I mean .. I shouldn't be warped half way across a zone to "escape" a round of hits.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Tweak ideas.. make it so you actually have a HUGE short burst of mitiagation increase or even avoidance &amp;nbsp;to avoid income melee damage.. and just warp around the target .. even with in 5 feet of the point of original activation loc.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;No raid or group Tank is going to let me use this&amp;nbsp;AA if the mob is going to chase me around a huge&amp;nbsp;room never mind a zone!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Also, instead of standing at a&amp;nbsp;new location for a full&amp;nbsp;tick .. maybe double the amount of jumps and half the duration you are there.. this would exemplify the dimentional instability yet, keep the duration the same... you'd also only be able to cast fast nukes ( instant only maybe ).&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
